reviewText:
The Italia release of Mia and Me Season 1 Volume 2 contains episodes 7 to 11 and it's only the Italian dubbed version.
In the magical world of Centopia, there's a Blossom Tree.

As much as I liked this animated DVD, there's no point on importing the Italian dubbed version because in France their dual-layer DVD releases actually has the English version in 5.1.
couldnt see the dvd, not zoned for USA
